1
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:48,360
Who are you?

2
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,480
You won't stop, huh?

3
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,480
Where's the blond?

4
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:51,200
Is he your dad?

5
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,320
You keep looking for him.

6
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,360
What are you waiting for?

7
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:54,080
Get him!

8
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:55,920
Stop, stop, stop.

9
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:56,520
Bro.

10
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:57,360
Easy.

11
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,320
Easy, bro.

12
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,080
Look,

13
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:02,000
there are so many blonds in this internet cafe.

14
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,760
How do I know which one you're looking for?

15
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:04,489
Why don't you

16
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,840
look for him yourself?

17
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:14,520
Get him.

18
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,400
Bro,

19
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,040
let's talk it out.

20
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,380
Where is the video?

21
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,120
You keep asking for a video.

22
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,480
What video is it?

23
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,520
You mean adult videos, right?

24
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,320
I have them.

25
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,440
Just tell me,

26
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,280
Japanese or Western?

27
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,440
If you don't like them,

28
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,880
don't hit me.

29
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,079
Look, bro,

30
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:01,640
I really don't know what video you're talking about.

31
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,300
Even if you beat me to death...

32
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,530
It's just a normal epileptic seizure.

33
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,329
I've already dealt with it.

34
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:37,040
As long as he doesn't bite his tongue, he'll be fine.

35
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,280
He should wake up soon.

36
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,079
Thank you.

37
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,180
I've been looking for you.

38
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:45,960
That explains it.

39
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,520
No wonder it's such a coincidence.

40
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,400
I left in a hurry earlier.

41
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,200
I'll transfer the medical bill to you.

42
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,530
I'm looking for you because of your wound.

43
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,000
If the foreign object in your body

44
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,160
is definitely not an implanted artificial organ,

45
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,440
then it's very dangerous for it to stay inside you.

46
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,880
It might press against your organs

47
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,200
and cause internal bleeding.

48
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,000
Furthermore,

49
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,040
if it contains any toxic substances,

50
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,640
once it breaks and spreads,

51
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,440
the consequences would be unimaginable.

52
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:09,120
So you need to take this seriously.

53
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,450
Go to the hospital and get it removed ASAP.

54
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,760
Okay, I got it.

55
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,200
But I have more important things to do right now.

56
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,040
I'll go later.

57
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:17,500
What could be more important than your life?

58
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,520
You're fine now.

59
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,280
No, bro.

60
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:49,080
What exactly do you want?

61
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,159
Where is the video?

62
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,200
I already told you.

63
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,480
I really don't know about any video.

64
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,840
Why don't you believe me?

65
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,840
Besides, I won't say anything else.

66
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,400
I am a grateful person.

67
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,480
Didn't you two just save my life?

68
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,200
Right?

69
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,440
So I definitely wouldn't lie to you.

70
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,480
It hurts, bro.

71
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,440
It hurts so much.

72
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,040
Let go.

73
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:12,840
Easy, bro.

74
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,400
Bro, I don't even have a girlfriend yet.

75
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,520
Bro, let go.

76
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,980
I'll give it to you.

77
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,360
Help!

78
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,200
Help!

79
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,400
Guys,

80
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,720
isn't she pale?

81
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,600
Animals.

82
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:45,200
We were just filming.

83
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,400
We didn't do anything to her.

84
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:48,760
Really.

85
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,480
I found the video.

86
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,160
But the girl in the video was...

87
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,320
Find all backups.

88
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:04,520
Find out who ordered Blondie to do this.

89
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,960
Where are the backups?

90
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,000
I swear,

91
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,520
really.

92
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,600
This is the only copy,

93
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,400
just this one,

94
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,600
really.

95
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,200
Look at me now,

96
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,440
I have no reason to lie to you, bro.

97
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,800
Then tell me,

98
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,940
who ordered you to do this?

99
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,960
I can't say that, bro.

100
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,840
That person said

101
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,240
if I sell him out,

102
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,240
he will kill me.

103
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,760
I beg you, bro,

104
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,760
don't force me, okay?

105
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,080
I beg you,

106
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:37,200
don't force me, okay?

107
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,100
Record this for me.

108
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,180
Take it off.

109
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,000
I will.

110
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,240
I will.

111
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,180
Keep taking it off.

112
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,800
Take this off too.

113
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,400
Still taking things off?

114
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,280
Take it off.

115
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,820
I'll give you two choices now.

116
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:38,200
The first is that I post this video of you online.

117
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,120
The second

118
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,159
is that you tell me

119
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,440
who put you up to this.

120
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,730
Why are you still following me?

121
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,340
I just got off work and have nothing to do.

122
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,920
Plus, you're injured.

123
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,880
I'm afraid you'll be in danger.

124
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:05,040
Besides, he has epilepsy.

125
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:08,300
It's always good to have an extra doctor around.

126
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,560
We've never met in person.

127
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:16,540
We only contacted each other through this game.

128
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,480
Show me your chat history.

129
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,680
I was playing a game at that time.

130
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,320
Then he added me as a friend.

131
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,799
He said he put the money in the trash can at that internet cafe.

132
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,880
Then I went over to check, and it was actually there.

133
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:37,400
He said he'd give me another 30,000 when it's done.

134
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,320
So I agreed.

135
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,159
I helped him shoot the video.

136
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,200
Then after shooting the video,

137
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,480
I put it at the location he designated.

138
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:47,170
After that, there was no more contact.

139
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,440
This game name should be random.

140
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,840
The game account is also newly registered.

141
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,880
I guess he registered this game account

142
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:58,520
just to hire me to shoot a video this way.

143
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,240
Xiaojie, help me check someone.

144
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,560
I'll give you a game account.

145
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:11,960
Help me check this person's personal identity information.

146
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,440
Bro.

147
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,880
If there's nothing else for me,

148
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,480
I'll leave first.

149
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:30,840
It's okay.

150
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,720
With rich practical experience and professional knowledge, entering the 1980s, Li Shengfa faced dual challenges in family and career.

151
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,480
working in a state-owned electronics factory, formally embarking on the path of electronic technology.

152
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:46,580
He eagerly learned professional knowledge and participated in various electronic production competitions.

153
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,840
There's a little situation here.

154
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:05,240
The person who hired the blonde guy has very strong anti-reconnaissance ability.

155
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,700
They contacted each other through the game.

156
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,460
Don't tell me this.

157
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:12,040
I don't have enough time.

158
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,360
I need some time.

159
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,480
Games have rules.

160
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,960
You can't break them.

161
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,180
And I won't either.

162
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,560
Power outage.

163
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:58,500
Are you going to keep following me like this?

164
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,370
Where are you going?

165
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,760
Follow me if you want,

166
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,760
or just leave.

167
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:07,010
Stop talking nonsense.

168
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:41,960
Wait a minute.

169
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:48,080
I gave your CT report

170
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,160
to a senior of mine at a top-tier hospital.

171
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:52,040
He is an expert in the imaging department.

172
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:53,440
He replied to my message.

173
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,400
He suspects it's a metal object.

174
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,280
I think it might be a tool left behind

175
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,680
by the doctor by accident when you had your surgery.

176
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:02,640
Or you can try to remember again.

177
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:03,160
Okay.

178
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:03,920
I got it.

179
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,600
Hello.

180
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,600
Hello, sir.

181
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,000
You have to line up here first.

182
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,720
I'm not lining up.

183
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,840
My matter is very urgent.

184
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,880
I want to report something to you.

185
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:11,200
I went traveling for two days,

186
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,400
and when I got back, everything in my fridge was rotten.

187
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,800
You didn't notify me in advance.

188
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:15,480
And I didn't owe any bills.

189
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,520
Why was there a power outage?

190
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:16,960
Right?

191
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,440
Calm down.

192
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,240
Of course I'm agitated.

193
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,800
I had thousands of yuan worth of Wagyu beef in the fridge.

194
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:21,840
My wife bought it.

195
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,920
My wife has been mad at me for days because of this.

196
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,520
You need to explain it properly to her.

197
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,280
Sir.

198
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,560
I just heard what you said.

199
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,720
Let me check on the computer for you

200
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,380
to see what exactly happened.

201
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,800
Please tell me your address and the time.

202
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,360
Qingyuan Neighborhood, September 8th.

203
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:36,800
Okay.

204
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,520
According to our records,

205
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:43,200
Qingyuan Neighborhood

206
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:45,320
hasn't had any power outages recently.

207
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,400
On September 8th,

208
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,880
only the area east of the intersection of Huaizhong Road and Fangbei Street,

209
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:49,840
up to Beicun,

210
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,840
experienced a brief power outage.

211
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,600
That was because of a damaged transformer,

212
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,560
and emergency repairs took two hours.

213
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:56,160
Thank you.

214
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:21,880
Zhang Jianming

215
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:21,960
Production Team
